(124, 1, '2015-05-07 12:19:37', '2015-05-07 12:19:37', '<p style="color: #eab040; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;">NAMANGAN 2-TIBBIYOT KOLLEJI 2015 -2016 O’QUV YILI UCHUN QUYIDAGI MUTAXASSISLIKLAR BO’YICHA TALABALAR QABULINI E’LON QILADI</p>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/Nammed-college.uz/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/jadval.png"><img class="  wp-image-112 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/Nammed-college.uz/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/jadval-300x132.png" alt="jadval" width="440" height="239" /></a>\r\n<p style="color: #eab040; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;">NAMANGAN 2-TIBBIYOT KOLLEJIGA HUJJAT TOPSHIRADIGAN ABITURIENTLARNING KERAKLI HUJJATLARI</p>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="color: #4e3f42; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; font-family: Arial; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;">1. Direktor nomiga ariza\r\n2. 9-sinfni tamomlaganligi to‘g‘risidagi shahodatnoma (asli)\r\n3. 086-U shaklidagi tibbiy ma''lkmotnoma\r\n4. Yashash joyidan ma''lumotnoma\r\n5. 3x4 shaklidagi 6 dona fotosurat\r\n6. Tug‘ilganlik haqidagi guvoxnoma yoki pasport nusxasi\r\n7. Tashxis markazining tavsiyanomasi\r\n8. Respublika fan olimpiadasi g‘olibligini tasdiqlovchi hujjat\r\n\r\n<p style="color: #eab040; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; font-family: Arial; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;">KOLLEJ MANZILI:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; font-family: Arial; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Manzilimiz: Namangan shahri, Go‘zal dahasi, 14-uy, Telefonlar: (8-369) 237-03-51, Faks: (8-369)237-21-95\r\nE-mail: nam.n2tk@.markaz.uz\r\nMo‘ljal: Respublika shoshilinch tibbiy yordam markazi Namangan viloyati filiali.\r\n2-Chorsu-Go‘zal, 10-Hamza-Go‘zal yo‘nalishidagi avtobus marshrutlari', 'Abiturientlar uchun', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '106-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-07 12:19:37', '2015-05-07 12:19:37', '', 106, 'http://localhost/Nammed-college.uz/2015/05/07/106-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
