(272, 1, '2015-05-10 09:06:58', '2015-05-10 09:06:58', '<p style="font: 20px Times New Roman; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 30px;" align="justify">O’zbekistonda shaxslarning ayrim guruhlarini ambulatoriya sharoitida davolanish uchun dori vositalari bilan imtiyozli (bepul) ta''minlash tartibini takomillashtirish maqsadida Sog’liqni saqlash vazirligi va Moliya vazirligining 2013 yil 8 noyabrdagi 27 va 103-sonli qarori bilan tasdiqlangan ambulatoriyada davolanishda imtiyozli ta''minlash uchun mo’ljallangan dori vositalarining ro’yxatiga qo’shimchalar kiritish bo’yicha qaror loyihasi tayyorlandi va 8 ta dori vositasi va 1 ta dori vositasi shakli qo’shimcha kiritildi.</p>\r\n<p style="font: 20px Times New Roman; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 30px;" align="justify"><a href="http://localhost/Nammed-college.uz/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/1431105986_02.jpg"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-271 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/Nammed-college.uz/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/1431105986_02-300x199.jpg" alt="1431105986_02" width="430" height="258" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="font: 20px Times New Roman; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 30px;" align="justify">Bu haqda SSV matbuot xizmati xabar bermoqda.Uzbekistan Today’ning xabar berishicha, endi O’zbekistondagi yolg’iz qariyalar, Ikkinchi jahon urushi qatnashchilari va mehnat fronti faxriylari ambulatoriya sharoitida davolanish uchun quyidagi sakkiz dori vositasini imtiyozli olishlari mumkin:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman;">Pentoeritritil tetranitrat (tabletka – 10 mg) – antianginal vosita;</li>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman; line-height: 30px;">Spirinolakton (tabletka – 25 mg) – diuretik vosita;</li>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman; line-height: 30px;">Piratsetam (in''yeksii qorishmasi – 200 mg/ml 5 ml) – nootrop vosita;</li>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman;">Pentoksifillin (tabletka – 100 mg; 400 mg; 600 mg) – periferiya qon aylanishini                  yaxshilaydigan vosita;</li>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman; line-height: 30px;">Emoksipin (ko’z tomchilari – 1% 5 ml; 10 mg/ml 1 ml) – oftalmologiyada                          qo’llaniladigan vosita;</li>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman; line-height: 30px;">Ambroksol (tabletka – 30 mg) – balg’am ko’chiradigan vosita;</li>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman; line-height: 30px;">Glimeperid (tabletka – 1 mg; 2 mg) – qandli diabetga qarshi vosita;</li>\r\n	<li style="font: 20px Times New Roman; line-height: -25px;">Finasterid (tabletka – 5 mg) – antiadrogen vosita.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p align="right">Manba:kun.uz</p>', 'O’zbekistonda imtiyozli dori vositalari ro’yxati kengaytirildi', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '213-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-10 09:06:58', '2015-05-10 09:06:58', '', 213, 'http://localhost/Nammed-college.uz/2015/05/10/213-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
