height: 30px; text-indent: 20px;" align="justify">Tuzuvchi MMIBDO’: R.Mamajonov</p>', 'Namangan 2-tibbiyot kollejida «14 yanvar-Vatan ximoyachilari kuni» munosabati bilan o''tkaziladigan  harbiy vatanparvarlik mavzusidagi tadbir', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '322-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-05 05:58:23', '2015-06-05 05:58:23', '', 322, 'http://localhost/Nammed-college.uz/2015/06/05/322-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
